criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Meet the diagnosis of severe aplastic anemia(SAA-I);
2. Not enrolled in other clinical trials;
3. Patients from 6 years old to 50 years old;
4. Sign informed consent form.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Pancytopenia attributing to other disorders,such as actue arrest of hemopoiesis,myelofibrosis and ect;
2. Severe comorbidities associated with cardio-cerebrovascular,liver and kidney or psychosis;
3. Associate with severe arrhythmia,such as rapid atrial fibrillation,atrial flutter,paroxysmal ventricular tachycardia and ect;
4. Associate with active peptic ulcer or other hemorrhagic disease;
5. Women in pregnancy, preparation for pregnancy or breast feeding period;
6. Allergic constitution;
7. Nearly three months have enrolled in other clinical trials or be enrolling in other clinical trials.
